# Title: Service Installed By Unusual Client - Security
# Author: Tim Rauch (Nextron Systems), Elastic (idea)
# Date: 2022-09-15
# Level: high
# Description: Detects a service installed by a client which has PID 0 or whose parent has PID 0
# MITRE Tactic: Persistence
# Tags: attack.persistence, attack.privilege-escalation, attack.t1543
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules/windows/builtin/security/win_security_service_installation_by_unusal_client.yml

EventID=4697 ClientProcessId=0 OR ParentProcessId=0